x4freetext: CV28
In each case four stacks were irradiated. Each stack
consisted of up to 50 thin foils of target and monitor
materials of high purity.
The activity of each foil was determined via
gamma-ray spectroscopy using a 32 cm3 Ge(Li) detector.
